        <p n="1">Fortune!</p>
        <p n="1-2">To the glorious Perumāṉaṭikaḷ of Tirukkaḻukkuṉṟam.</p>
        <p n="2-8">That which Naraciṅkapōttaracar, the conqueror of Vātāpi, gave, as tax-free land <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>puṟam</foreign>
          </supplied> for the purpose of worship <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>vaḻipāṭu</foreign>
          </supplied>, to the Perumāṉaṭikaḷ of the <foreign>mūlasthāna</foreign> at Tirukkaḵukkuṉṟam on the glorious hill of Tirukkaḻukkuṉṟam <gap reason="illegible"/> in the Kaḷattūrkōṭṭam.</p>
